WEBVTT

00:05.464 --> 00:07.216
<i>What brings you home?</i>

00:07.216 --> 00:09.843
<i>- Kidnapping.</i>
- Oh, fuck!

00:09.843 --> 00:12.387
<i>Nothing else to call
what they did to that kid.</i>

00:12.387 --> 00:14.640
<i>Do you think
that's why you came back?</i>

00:14.640 --> 00:16.475
<i>'Cause it reminded you?</i>

00:16.475 --> 00:18.268
<i>Henry?</i>

00:18.268 --> 00:20.729
<i>No frostbite.
You been inside somewhere?</i>

00:24.316 --> 00:26.235
I've had a beautiful experience.

00:28.028 --> 00:30.530
- And I heard it.
- What?

00:30.530 --> 00:33.408
<i>You're saying my dad
believed he could hear God?</i>

00:33.408 --> 00:35.410
Other heres. Other nows.

00:35.410 --> 00:38.622
All possible pasts,
all possible presents...

00:38.622 --> 00:40.541
the schisma is
the sound of the universe

00:40.541 --> 00:42.668
trying to reconcile them.

00:42.668 --> 00:45.587
<i>"Never again
let him see the light of day."</i>

00:47.089 --> 00:49.132
<i>That's what God told me.</i>

00:49.132 --> 00:50.717
You know me.

00:50.717 --> 00:53.220
I don't know anything about you.

00:53.220 --> 00:55.597
You do.
And I know you.

00:55.597 --> 00:57.683
Out there in the woods.

00:57.683 --> 00:59.184
That's where you died.

01:02.229 --> 01:03.647
Do you hear it?

01:03.647 --> 01:04.940
We have to go to the woods.

01:04.940 --> 01:06.608
Why did you ask for me?

01:06.608 --> 01:07.943
<i>Young man...</i>

01:07.943 --> 01:09.403
who are you?

01:09.403 --> 01:10.821
Henry Deaver.

01:16.910 --> 01:20.998
<i>God turned His back
on this place.</i>

01:25.919 --> 01:29.590
<i>Abandoned us...
that's what people say.</i>

01:32.259 --> 01:35.721
<i>Or they say
He's punishing us for our sins,</i>

01:35.721 --> 01:37.639
<i>like Sodom and Gomorrah.</i>

01:41.268 --> 01:43.854
<i>You remember
the helicopter crash.</i>

01:46.690 --> 01:50.277
<i>How about the school bus?</i>

